title: 705. Breaking Down Rookies After Preseason Week 1
itunes:title: 705. Breaking Down Rookies After Preseason Week 1
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this special show, the guys do a breakdown of the first-round rookie quarterbacks after Preseason Week 1. To wrap up the show, the duo look at all the other rookies that impressed them.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
